= mysql2-keepalive

== Description

TCP keepalive extension for Mysql2

== Install

gem install mysql2-keepalive

== Example

  require 'mysql2'
  require 'mysql2/keepalive'
  
  client = Mysql2::Client.new(:host => 'mysql.example.com', :username => 'scott', :password => 'tiger')
  
  client.keepalive = true
  client.keepidle = 15
  client.keepintvl = 5
  client.keepcnt = 3
